EN: Tigers have strong hearing and vision.

ZH: 虎是一种濒危物种。
EN: The tiger is an endangered species.

ZH: 孩子们喜欢虎的卡通形象。
EN: Kids love the cartoon image of tigers.

ZH: 虎是很有地盘意识的动物。
EN: Tigers are very territorial animals.

ZH: 虎在水里游得很快。
EN: Tigers swim very fast in the water.

ZH: 这只虎正在悄悄接近猎物。
EN: The tiger is stealthily approaching its prey.

ZH: 虎的呼唤声很洪亮。
EN: The roar of a tiger is very loud.

ZH: 虎是动物王国中的霸主。
EN: Tigers are the kings of the animal kingdom.

ZH: 虎是非常优秀的狩猎者。
EN: Tigers are excellent hunters.
